cat << EOF
ParaGUI is a cross-platform high-level application framework and GUI library.
It can be compiled on various platforms (Linux, Win32, BeOS, MacOS, ...)
ParaGUI's cross-platform nature is completely based on the 
Simple DirectMedia Layer (SDL) .
EOF
